   THE CLINTON CRISIS
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON _ CINCINNATI and BOSTON _ President Clinton attends
fund-raisers in Cincinnati and Boston. (Deans, Cox News Service).
</P>
<P>
   Eds: A story will be filed after the Cincinnati appearance and
then retopped from Boston.
