Holyfield. Remember the week that he attended a religious revival,
opened a new clothing line and showed up at several events? He won
handily. But his focus will be put to the test Saturday night
because he also is an unofficial promoter and is back in his
hometown at the zenith of his career. (Schultz, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
