<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    RELIGIOUS, CONGRESSIONAL LEADERS PUSH FOR PASSAGE OF AFRICA
TRADE BILL
 &HT;    Moving in both the (i) International and (f) Financial
categories.
 &HT;    By NICHOLE MONROE 
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service 
