   INTERNATIONAL (``i'' category)
</P>
<P>
   MEXICO-MASSACRE (Mexico City) _ Gunmen pull three families from
their beds, line them up against a wall and kill at least 19 men,
women and children near a popular Baja California resort. Three
others are seriously wounded. The head of the of the households
grew marijuana for the Tijuana drug cartel, officials said. By
DUDLEY ALTHAUS.
</P>
