THIS IS A HOUSTON CHRONICLE TEST
</HEADLINE>
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients)
<TEXT>
<P>
   HOUSTON _ This is a Houston Chronicle test. This is a Houston
Chronicle test. This is a Houston Chronicle test. This is a Houston
Chronicle test.
</P>
